    <div class = 'subheading'>
        What are the Applications?
        </div>
    <div class = 'description'>
        This new Electronic Vital Sign Monitor would allow medical professionals to allocate more visual focus on patients rather than on the electronic monitors. This innovation allows them to give their undivided attention to the patient rather than splitting their field of vision between the patient and the monitor screen. This is just one application, but the ability to dynamically sonifying timbres has implications to advance data sonification throughout the  medical field.

